{"tid":1788271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被埋了在雪中，點出返去？","createTime":"2019-12-18T14:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T05:32:01.000Z","uid":288968,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1174c6201dd5b40f9003fe2472e72aab2f0977","tid":1788271,"uid":288968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"到底我係咪唔應該存在係呢個世界<br />\n點解身邊嘅所有人都會因為我受傷<br />\n<br />\n好大雪...坐咗係街唔敢返酒店<br />\n有無人想傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37dc0cfa3dc548741007c336ef3e61118d70ca5","tid":1788271,"uid":29153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"435f4885848e50d567c6c8d4ed0b891fd50316b8","tid":1788271,"uid":288968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37dc0cfa3dc548741007c336ef3e61118d70ca5","tid":1788271,"uid":29153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"難得屋企去旅行<br />\n又吵到頭家要散咁濟了.....<br />\n<br />\n對上一次同屋企人去旅行<br />\n又係呢個結果<br />\n用咗5年先攸補到<br />\n<br />\n然後，其實唔係今日先發現<br />\n有問題嘅唔係佢地<br />\n而係自己<br />\n唔止屋企人....<br />\n每一個係自己身邊，夠接近自己嘅人<br />\n都會比我嘅情緒嚇親<br />\n<br />\n好多時候，我都好唔想係咁<br />\n其實無次傷害咗人<br />\n我都唔知點解又會咁樣"},{"pid":"e8d75413a0b7151fa508a1b066ca0c37e88cb0d2","tid":1788271,"uid":322454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"你未免太睇高你自己<br />\n<br />\n你冇能力成為令你身邊的人受傷的主因，其他原因你冇考慮過<br />\n<br />\n如果真係你令其他人受傷，你味負返責任<br />\n做咩都有成本，冇免費午餐<br />\n<br />\n你入酒店先，感冒自殘都會令愛你的人受傷"},{"pid":"bf26313276fc0e80a7c3d297b3511dcb9568adf4","tid":1788271,"uid":288968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"435f4885848e50d567c6c8d4ed0b891fd50316b8","tid":1788271,"uid":288968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37dc0cfa3dc548741007c336ef3e61118d70ca5","tid":1788271,"uid":29153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"？"